                            <comment id="14456164" author="agudian" created="Sat, 11 Oct 2014 15:03:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This may look more like an issue of the JRE that was used here. Probably, the GC-Info printed by the VM is not routed through the System.out, but directly from the native JVM code to stdout.&lt;/p&gt;

